{"tid":2434354,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"菠蘿整果醬 用來沖水果茶 #吃爆台灣鳳梨Challenge","createTime":"2021-03-05T12:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T05:13:30.000Z","uid":392377,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"64506933387b0b206d574103f1b85177c21ae35a","tid":2434354,"uid":392377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T12:55:23.000Z","msg":"//台灣出口大陸的鳳梨近年來多次被檢出介殼蟲，中國大陸以此為由，2月26日突襲宣布3月1日起暫停台灣鳳梨進口。總統蔡英文在臉書強力表達譴責，指控大陸單方面暫停輸入台灣鳳梨是「非正常的貿易考量」，並呼籲全台一起挺農民、吃鳳梨，發起一系列「#吃爆台灣鳳梨challenge」、「#自由鳳梨」等活動//<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">菠蘿果醬 ft. 水果茶</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EjYYFsGYIwE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEjYYFsGYIwE&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=64da73e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EjYYFsGYIwE</a><br />\n利申：英國未買到台灣菠蘿，台灣超市話要空運，但台灣-英國機去到三月尾都無停航。所以我用既係Costa Rica菠蘿，行咗五間都係青BB，哩個係最黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gt7UPxW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGt7UPxW.png&h=b2ce4452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W72Np6d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW72Np6d.png&h=93003e1f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n國民團結爆買拯救食材不是夢！2012年意大利人爆買行動成功拯救在地震中損毀過億的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />parmigiano-reggiano (&quot;parmesan&quot;)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dzd5bMf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDzd5bMf.png&h=6ebff786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n整完可以整水果茶！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個concept係好似柚子蜜咁，溝梳打水就變菠蘿梳打<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n4bB2SY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn4bB2SY.png&h=8f587434&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fnog2SX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffnog2SX.png&h=2a1a19b0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Instagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/cooking.therapy1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcooking.therapy1%2F&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=6d614df2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/cooking.therapy1/</a><br />\n<br />\n//中國大陸是台灣出口農產品外銷最大的市場，幾乎佔九成以上的台灣外銷訂單。譬如前幾年，台灣前高雄市長韓國瑜便是以農產品加深加快出口中國大陸，遊客入台買土產（鳳梨酥等）的「貨出去，人進來，高雄發大財」口號，掀起「韓流」。<br />\n但如今，隨著韓國瑜被罷免，兩岸高度緊張的大背景下，中國這個超級市場已能夠大量且快速生產農作物，將來是否還要繼續讓台灣水果進口或禁止哪些農產品進口，手上擁有充足籌碼。外界認為鳳梨事件可能只是個開始。<br />\n為了回應此次鳳梨風波，台灣總統蔡英文也發起「全民吃鳳梨」行動，許多大企業團體及組織（譬如台灣高鐵）都認養鳳梨，並表示將全力協助農民度過難關。美國在台最高行政單位，美國在台協會（AIT）也加入聲援台灣鳳梨，讓此事政治意味更濃。//<br />\n//現在台灣農業要做的就是「分散風險」，因為現有水果外銷市場「幾乎全部」都輸往中國大陸。「這次是鳳梨，之後遇到的問題不就是釋迦或蓮霧，而且，明年希望採收的鳳梨，是在去年就播種，因此明年要面對的問題可能更大。」<br />\n事實上，據台灣農業經濟學者焦鈞統計，自2018年至2019年一年間，台鳳梨出口中國就遽增2萬公噸，來到5萬公噸的高點，打破紀錄。焦鈞說，台灣確實有需要檢討將全部雞蛋都放在待一籃子的策略：「過去二年鳳梨出口爆增卻未能及早預警，甚至將之視為外銷政績，這是首先要檢討之處。」//<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-56278195\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-56278195&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=e46773ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-56278195&h=5ba4f11a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-56278195</a><br />\n//台灣鳳梨遭到中國政治性抵制，卻意外幫台灣做了免費的國際宣傳，日本媒體不但連日報導台灣鳳梨新聞，日本名人也爭在推特貼文挺台灣鳳梨，連本身也是鳳梨產地的日本石垣市市長中山義隆也推文挺台灣鳳梨，還說石垣島的鳳梨是90年前從台灣傳過去的。<br />\n台灣鳳梨最近在日本成為熱門話題，日本雅虎新聞今天的國際新聞點閱排行榜前5名，台灣鳳梨新聞佔了兩則，一則是朝日新聞報導，台灣「爆買」鳳梨與中國對抗，另一則是共同社台北發出的蔡英文總統感謝日本朋友買鳳梨，報導中還指中國的做法可能得到反效果。//<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/03/03/3455545_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F03%2F03%2F3455545_1_1.jpg&h=9f7a2376&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1b8738c44ab35291be7ccdf2972712286a145d","tid":2434354,"uid":392196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T12:58:45.000Z","msg":"十卜you"},{"pid":"3e0d3143f8a808574173cce07d6335b0c9f98e70","tid":2434354,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:02:17.000Z","msg":"溝落kombucha到做second fermentation 應該唔差<br />\n又可以食少啲糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9c47b505ea834ea377c753869272b149054ac6","tid":2434354,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be3bdd98b349c81d76df1fe4114e50f92cecd9b","tid":2434354,"uid":392377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e0d3143f8a808574173cce07d6335b0c9f98e70","tid":2434354,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:02:17.000Z","msg":"溝落kombucha到做second fermentation 應該唔差<br />\n又可以食少啲糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:39:30.000Z","msg":"大鄉里未飲過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪要啲特別用具來做fermentation<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf42f9de4ddfcfc474295361b12aed3550817cf1","tid":2434354,"uid":392377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c9c47b505ea834ea377c753869272b149054ac6","tid":2434354,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:39:47.000Z","msg":"Thank god<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e5abe61f802abb856f066f8a17ab4b7bb4f3b2","tid":2434354,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4be3bdd98b349c81d76df1fe4114e50f92cecd9b","tid":2434354,"uid":392377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e0d3143f8a808574173cce07d6335b0c9f98e70","tid":2434354,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:02:17.000Z","msg":"溝落kombucha到做second fermentation 應該唔差<br />\n又可以食少啲糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:39:30.000Z","msg":"大鄉里未飲過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪要啲特別用具來做fermentation<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:56:18.000Z","msg":"有人肯share菌種畀你就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用玻璃樽就可以發酵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發得夠耐會有啲汽水feel解渴一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b24ef20efd2a817a2482135d0fca4843b4827c2","tid":2434354,"uid":392377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2e5abe61f802abb856f066f8a17ab4b7bb4f3b2","tid":2434354,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4be3bdd98b349c81d76df1fe4114e50f92cecd9b","tid":2434354,"uid":392377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e0d3143f8a808574173cce07d6335b0c9f98e70","tid":2434354,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20