 />\n似係同一個老細開<br />\n係專賣台灣進口貨 (但有極少數貨品可能係台灣代理但中國製造 要留意)<br />\n有時見佢賣啲台灣生果 例如椪柑 文旦柚<br />\n希望佢會入啲菠蘿啦"},{"pid":"3c3d6b9401f700e1e6e909137d2d743a26d9a885","tid":2434354,"uid":392377,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1f9d16969b2fc2c71c1cc485397b272662927a65","tid":2434354,"uid":218412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"69fefe2c1f857e9e4a4b5f93f4847818798a9fae","tid":2434354,"uid":392377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a29232728042c9e472e12df386d27eec0974b42d","tid":2434354,"uid":218412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔用蘋果用其他生果？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nG持 好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T15:44:12.000Z","msg":"橙都夾㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又係多果膠<br />\n摵完個皮 肉同皮掉埋落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n塊皮好似片入面檸檬皮咁煮，煮完就掉咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T20:27:24.000Z","msg":"其實係咩原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係唔使落魚膠都可以變gel？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T21:30:49.000Z","msg":"啲生果入面有果膠（pectin)<br />\n佢係啲生果會實淨嘅原因（所以蘋果多果膠，士多啤梨淋芝芝就無乜）<br />\n太熟就會被啲enzyme分解pectin（所以熟既生果會變淋）<br />\n<br />\nGel就係Pectin同自己痴埋一齊就變到個網咁<br />\n<br />\n煮jam嘅時候係發生緊哩啲事：<br />\n1. 你加熱既時候，哩啲pectin係生果到流出來<br />\n2. Pectin係水溶性，即係佢鐘意同水埋堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但你目的要佢自己同自己痴埋先做到個網。所要你就要相當多嘅糖，啲糖霸住啲水，咁啲水先唔再同pectin做朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 雖然水唔同pectin做朋友，但pectin都仲係唔肯同自己人痴埋，因為pectin本身帶負電，負負相拒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以你要檸檬（酸），酸會增加正電，中和咗咁pectin同pectin就終於可以做朋友痴埋一齊喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid