me":"2021-03-05T21:57:40.000Z","msg":"講番菠蘿<br />\n香港多年來賣嘅好似都係菲律賓為主<br />\n我諗強國菠蘿啲質素其實好唔掂<br />\n如果唔係使乜連台灣啲次貨都要買埋吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T23:46:42.000Z","msg":"btw 教協有得訂<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkptu.org/86413\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkptu.org%2F86413&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=4c170e37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkptu.org/86413</a><br />\n有大公報認證「教協不除，黃師難滅」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以G持"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T17:34:06.000Z","msg":"唔係會員點買<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"3c3d6b9401f700e1e6e909137d2d743a26d9a885","tid":2434354,"uid":392377,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T21:30:49.000Z","msg":"啲生果入面有果膠（pectin)<br />\n佢係啲生果會實淨嘅原因（所以蘋果多果膠，士多啤梨淋芝芝就無乜）<br />\n太熟就會被啲enzyme分解pectin（所以熟既生果會變淋）<br />\n<br />\nGel就係Pectin同自己痴埋一齊就變到個網咁<br />\n<br />\n煮jam嘅時候係發生緊哩啲事：<br />\n1. 你加熱既時候，哩啲pectin係生果到流出來<br />\n2. Pectin係水溶性，即係佢鐘意同水埋堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但你目的要佢自己同自己痴埋先做到個網。所要你就要相當多嘅糖，啲糖霸住啲水，咁啲水先唔再同pectin做朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 雖然水唔同pectin做朋友，但pectin都仲係唔肯同自己人痴埋，因為pectin本身帶負電，負負相拒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以你要檸檬（酸），酸會增加正電，中和咗咁pectin同pectin就終於可以做朋友痴埋一齊喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}